## ğŸ“Œ Supported Entities

| Entity | Example |
|------|--------|
| PAN | ABCDE1234F |
| Aadhaar | 2345 6789 0123 |
| Indian Phone | +91 9876543210 |
| Credit Card | 4111 1111 1111 1111 |
| UPI ID | rahul@upi |
| IFSC | HDFC0001234 |

